fields.name: Identity
fields.description: The client id of the identity which will be used to access key vault.

fields.name: KeyIdentifier
fields.description: Key vault uri to access the encryption key.

fields.name: KeyRotationEnabled
fields.description: Auto key rotation status for a CMK enabled registry.

fields.name: LastKeyRotationTimestamp
fields.description: Timestamp of the last successful key rotation.

fields.name: VersionedKeyIdentifier
fields.description: The fully qualified key identifier that includes the version of the key that is actually used for encryption.
